edu.regis.msse670.model.domain

Class WorldInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.regis.msse670.model.domain.Inventory
      • edu.regis.msse670.model.domain.WorldInventory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WorldInventory
extends Inventory
    WorldInventory is the lowest tier inventory in the inventory heirarchy. All other inventories must be stored within the WorldInventory, whether directly or as part of another inventory. The tier logic only allows a Storable to be stored in another inventory of the same tier or lower. WorldInventory is the only inventory that can accept every other item. There can only be a single WorldInventory at a time.

    1.0
